{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/dotdocument\/samselectdetailregion"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument"]]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument\/samSelectDetailRegion","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@F@samSelectDetailRegion","symbolKind":"func","title":"samSelectDetailRegion","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Function","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"}],"modules":[{"name":"DotDocument"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"preciseIdentifier":"c:I","text":"int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"const","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument\/sam_color_image","text":"SamColorImage","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@sam_color_image","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"image","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"const","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:I","text":"int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:I","text":"int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"selectedBoundingBox","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":");","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0 on success, or a non-zero error code on failure."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Analyzes the input image and identifies the most suitable 200x200 pixel"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"region (bounding box) with high level of details that intersects a given bounding box."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox"},{"type":"text","text":" is empty (width or height is 0), any region can be selected. Otherwise,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the selected region should have non-empty intersection with this bounding box. The selected region"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"should lie fully inside the input image."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If there is no region satisfying these conditions - if image width or height is smaller than 200"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox"},{"type":"text","text":" lies outside the image, the selected bounding box will be (0, 0, 200, 200)."}]},{"code":["                                  a bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height)."],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null},{"code":["                                  return, contains the bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height),","                                  where width and height are always set to 200."],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null}]}],"references":{"doc://DotDocument/documentation/DotDocument":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"version: 9.4.0","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","title":"DotDocument","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/dotdocument"},"doc://DotDocument/documentation/DotDocument/sam_color_image":{"title":"sam_color_image","url":"\/documentation\/dotdocument\/sam_color_image","fra